#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.ir_ui_view_3760
msgid ""
"Absolutely! We welcome players of all ages, though some rooms have minimum "
"age suggestions due to complexity or themes. <em>Curse of the Pharaoh</em> "
"is a great pick for families and younger players. Just check the age limit "
"listed for each room."
msgstr ""
"當然適合！我們歡迎所有年齡的玩家，不過部份房間由於主題性質或謎題複雜程度，可"
"能會有建議最低玩家年齡。如有需要，「法老王的詛咒」房間比較適合家庭及年紀較小"
"的玩家。請留意每個房間列明的年齡限制。<em></em>"

