msgid "Theme"
msgstr "主題"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This app makes scheduling intuitive for customers and efficient for your "
"team. Whether it’s a small group or a company team-building event, players "
"can choose their preferred slot, answer custom questions, and receive "
"instant confirmations. It’s all synced behind the scenes with room capacity."
msgstr ""
"此應用程式讓客戶可輕鬆自行預約，也讓你的團隊能夠高效率編排活動。無論是小組活"
"動，還是全公司大型團隊建設活動，參加者都可選擇心儀的時段，簡單回答自訂問題，"
"然後立即收到確認。所有資訊都會在後台與房間可用時間表同步更新。"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid "Track sales per staff member with <strong>session reports</strong>."
msgstr "查看<strong>營業時段報告</strong>，追蹤每位員工的銷售表現。"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>custom questions</strong> during booking to tailor the "
"experience (e.g. birthday surprise? team-building?)."
msgstr ""
"在預訂過程加入<strong>自訂問題</strong>，提供度身設計的客戶體驗（例如，詢問是"
"否生日驚喜、團隊建立活動等）。"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>pipelines</strong> to track enquiry &gt; quote &gt; contract "
"&gt; event."
msgstr ""
"使用<strong>管道</strong>功能，追蹤查詢 &gt; 報價 &gt; 合約 &gt; 活動的工作進"
"程。"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.ir_ui_view_3247
msgid "Useful Links"
msgstr "有用的連結"

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:escape_rooms.appointment_type_1
msgid "Victorian Detective Mystery"
msgstr ""

